706283f-a.text:
Pineapple Street, east from Henry to Fulton Streets. In the background is the S.E. corner of Fulton and Concord Streets. Also seen is the Fulton Street Elevated line of the B.M.T.
April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
